name: 2022 11th International Conference on Software and Information Engineering
content: Publication: Submissions will be peer reviewed by both the conference scientific committees and journal editorial board. All registered and presented papers will be published in ICSIE 2022 Conference Proceedings by ACM (ISBN: 978-1-4503-9706-3), which will be submitted for \*EI Compendex\*, \*Scopus\* et al.
